{"tid":506871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警逛深水埗涉高買　偷值$29耳筒衰咗","createTime":"2017-12-22T15:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T09:43:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"94b3ff553b52c34b1dee840e8b6f905ad6d60217","tid":506871,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"一名54歲姓張休班警員於今晚7時許，到深水埗福華街161-175號一店舖選購一些手機配件，惟離開時被39歲姓黃男店員發現他身上藏有一對價值29元的耳筒，但未有付款。職員於是報警，警方到場經初步調查後，以涉嫌盜竊拘捕張，他已獲准保釋候查，須於本月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，如任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理。案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"466caf01ec7a7e32f11334a8e2687c3cd10c3f1a","tid":506871,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171222/57616484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57616484&d=4MxJQVgQqs6CX8oCnslF2HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=33f81be8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57616484&h=a5d04748\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171222/57616484</a>"},{"pid":"1a033285c24fea40996b43db8a2dd06c29c5cf6d","tid":506871,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"差一年可以拎退休金，無左就正囉"},{"pid":"2271a73bbed44f5c553aa136f78fe859938ab902","tid":506871,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差一年可以拎退休金，無左就正囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e67b6620bc69b8724221d18409497c472b4737c","tid":506871,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":58,"score":-58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"高買咩年代詞"},{"pid":"c2d90bc18f3fe8280e354af54e4c683396c4012e","tid":506871,"uid":82851,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"ci